quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  15,32,"Qala ya ibleesu ma lakaalla takoona maAAa assajideen"
  15,33,"Qala lam akun li-asjuda libasharinkhalaqtahu min salsalin min hama-in masnoon"
  15,34,"Qala fakhruj minhafa-innaka rajeem"
  15,35,"Wa-inna AAalayka allaAAnata ila yawmiaddeen"
  15,36,"Qala rabbi faanthirneeila yawmi yubAAathoon"
  15,37,"Qala fa-innaka mina almunthareen"
  15,38,"Ila yawmi alwaqti almaAAloom"
  15,39,"Qala rabbi bima aghwaytaneelaozayyinanna lahum fee al-ardi walaoghwiyannahumajmaAAeen"
  15,40,"Illa AAibadaka minhumualmukhlaseen"
  15,41,"Qala hatha siratunAAalayya mustaqeem"
  15,42,"Inna AAibadee laysa laka AAalayhimsultanun illa mani ittabaAAaka mina alghaween"
  15,43,"Wa-inna jahannama lamawAAiduhum ajmaAAeen"
  15,44,"Laha sabAAatu abwabin likullibabin minhum juz-on maqsoom"
  15,45,"Inna almuttaqeena fee jannatinwaAAuyoon"
  15,46,"Odkhulooha bisalamin amineen"
  15,47,"WanazaAAna ma fee sudoorihimmin ghillin ikhwanan AAala sururin mutaqabileen"
  15,48,"La yamassuhum feeha nasabunwama hum minha bimukhrajeen"
  15,49,"Nabbi/ AAibadee annee anaalghafooru arraheem"
  15,50,"Waanna AAathabee huwa alAAathabual-aleem"
  15,51,"Wanabbi/hum AAan dayfi ibraheem"
